Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,==========Avant==========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.98,0:00:06.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然有一天 从天空掉下来一个蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.86,0:00:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏给这颗蛋中孵出的不可思议的生物命名为毛毛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.03,0:00:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它对夏来说是新的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.53,0:00:25.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与此同时 评议院在各公会之间建立了交换留学生制度
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.79,0:00:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏利用这个机会 在各公会之间四处询问有关毛毛的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.92,0:00:35.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却完全没有得到有用的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而这时 一行人受到评议院的委托
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.60,0:00:49.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和剑齿之虎一起调查在近海处突然出现的神秘岛屿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.52,0:00:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,评议院的判断是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.15,0:00:55.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是个岛屿非常危险
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.91,0:00:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.95,0:00:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,==========Main==========
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 已经祝福好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 到底有什么危险呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:52.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个岛上有未知生物的生命反应
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:56.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知是人还是动物的奇怪的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:02:59.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,产生于出现仅有几天的岛屿上…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:02.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一说的话 感觉确实有点危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才让我们去探查吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠岸后 我作为指挥官留在船上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登陆后 有什么情况就发信号弹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:14.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:28.68,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\pos(640,450)\fad(524,0}你来的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:33.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近才出现的岛屿为什么会有路？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会是这个岛以前有人类住过 但是后来沉没了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:42.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而现在 又突然浮上来了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 那个遗迹里说不定有什么线索
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得散发着一股很可疑的气息呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗洛也这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们分散开 调查一下周围的情况吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那个遗迹处汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 只是个森林嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱开始肚子饿了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:10.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 完全没有紧张感呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么在森林中会有贝壳？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:23.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这个贝壳有见过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:27.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛇姬之鳞的那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那个石板背面的一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 大家看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道这个就是在人鱼之踵那里看到的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.17,0:04:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是鱼哎 看起来好好吃的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:47.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会吃坏肚子的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是海里的东西连同岛屿一起上来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:52.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 露西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果之前这个岛是沉入海中的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:58.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么树木还能长得这么繁茂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:05:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还形成了森林
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里非比寻常这一点是毋庸置疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:18.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:22.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是遗迹的方向 我们快走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:23.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:30.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙就是生命反应的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 是海蛇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:37.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:42.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是海里的怪物 以前我曾经听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.03,0:05:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是陆地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信号弹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:14.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:29.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 妖精的尾巴和剑齿之虎已经登陆了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也快点前往那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掩护 准备炮击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:35.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾露莎 夏他们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那个遗迹中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:57.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像在外面的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 被关在里面了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚的声音是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.13,0:07:26.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是心脏跳动的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心脏的声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:33.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是有什么东西 在这里面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之我们也得想办法牵制一下那家伙才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.48,0:07:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 否则夏他们在里面的会被压扁的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 我们上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.94,0:07:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冰加农炮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.82,0:07:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗格
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:07:58.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影龙的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:07:59.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白龙的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:10.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是斯汀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗格也很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 这个 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和鸠拉给我们看的一样的古代文字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温蒂？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道为什么…身体…动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被攻击了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多兰巴尔特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然就倒下了 完全不知道怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:08:57.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦你将她们带去船上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:08:59.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 但是你们怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管那么多 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:16.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西 再不快点就要被压扁了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啊 但是有那么多的文字…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:26.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是有点像心脏的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心脏？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:31.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个岛是活的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:36.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哇 这个烟是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛毛 你是什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:46.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:49.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 烟？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾露莎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:56.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:09:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗洛修
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:08.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好恶心 头好晕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:09.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗洛也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:14.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事 发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.09,0:10:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:22.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岛上到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾露莎他们正在和怪物交战中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两个人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 说是突然就倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道这个情况…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:33.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么病毒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:35.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这两个人搬到船舱里去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉哈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没好吗 露西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:52.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 那里也写着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「光」「恩惠」「树木」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.80,0:10:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:01.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「守护」「灾祸」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.51,0:11:04.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「毒」「净化」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.22,0:11:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毒？净化？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:10.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毒？这个是毒气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 照一下天花板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:18.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:23.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和在蛇姬之鳞看见的文献画的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西他们呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏他们也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子不能动的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.04,0:11:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火龙的翼击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:55.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:11:59.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:01.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:07.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得可能会有什么线索 就从蛇姬之鳞借出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:18.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个形状 还有印象吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和蛇姬之鳞那里的石板是一个形状的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:26.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:35.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然表面的单词少了一半
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是也许这么做就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.11,0:12:39.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:46.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点啊 拉哈尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让这座岛沉下去吧…去联系评议院
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岛上还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:58.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须阻止病毒感染扩散到大陆去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:12:59.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.30,0:13:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果连你都被感染了的话 还有谁去传达消息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位…快点回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:19.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.94,0:13:22.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:26.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.86,0:13:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了 这个是植物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:31.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,植物？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.74,0:13:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「光」「恩惠」「树木」「光合作用」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「毒」「灾厄」「净化」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:49.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后是「植物」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:13:58.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「守护」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:10.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛毛？难道你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗洛修 雷库塔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 完全站不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 这个难道是病毒什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:23.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.05,0:14:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛毛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛毛？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守护…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.93,0:15:21.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 我是谁 我该做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.06,0:15:27.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然想到未来我会很害怕 但我会站出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:31.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为夏是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:34.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说我是「家人」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:15:58.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾露莎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:15:59.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灰！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,病毒…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:03.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,病毒？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个烟果然有毒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.36,0:16:08.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 都振作点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 那个烟不是毒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也在那里面碰到了烟 但是没被感染
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.12,0:16:25.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好相反
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛毛身体里出来的烟 才不是毒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放出病毒的是这个岛本身 那个是净化病毒的烟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,净化？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.72,0:16:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是毛毛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:47.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛毛应该不是动物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.11,0:16:49.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.90,0:16:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温蒂？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:17:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛毛一定是净化病毒的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,植物的神明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙一直在保护我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:18.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛毛 我们可不会让你一个人抢风头的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:23.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们上 哈比
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.56,0:17:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈比
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.73,0:17:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好毛毛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让它看看我们的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火龙的咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座岛自古以来就不断地上浮和下沉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:50.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而每当其上浮的时候 就会放出病毒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:55.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古代曾经有毫不知情的人在这座岛上建立了文明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.26,0:17:59.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而一直在帮助这些人的 就是毛毛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么难道现在也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.93,0:18:05.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是一直在持续净化病毒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.94,0:18:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛毛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红莲爆炎刃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.91,0:18:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏他们呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:25.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害啊 毛毛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛毛…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.43,0:18:49.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 毛毛 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.36,0:18:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:18:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岛在…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.36,0:19:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕了 夏！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.95,0:19:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岛开始下沉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得快点逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:05.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗洛也这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:08.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 毛毛 毛毛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:09.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了啊 毛毛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛毛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.43,0:19:23.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.97,0:19:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.85,0:19:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…会说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都忘了 但是 现在想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:37.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,语言和职责
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.82,0:19:38.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,职责？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 快起来 一起回家去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:44.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身体已经和树木一体化了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要和这个岛一起沉下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:54.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.08,0:19:58.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来把岛上的病毒吸收掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:20:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏就和大家一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 你也要一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:12.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不能再继续守护大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:16.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃走吧 是离别的时候了 夏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.81,0:20:20.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是离别啊 我不可能走的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:24.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛毛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.07,0:20:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛毛 毛毛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:32.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 我也是…妖精的尾巴…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.83,0:20:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.37,0:20:36.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…的一员吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是妖精的尾巴的同伴 是我们的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.22,0:20:48.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢…我很开心…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.18,0:20:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 回答我 回答我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.86,0:20:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.69,0:21:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.28,0:21:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛毛的…种子？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.83,0:21:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.01,0:21:35.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没能守护好那家伙 明明是家人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.06,0:21:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.44,0:21:43.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和遗迹上记载的古代文明那时候一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.78,0:21:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛毛是类似于那座岛的神明一样的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.95,0:21:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 而它也完成了自己的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.54,0:22:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天 还会再会的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.64,0:22:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别忘了关门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.39,0:22:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.39,0:22:19.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望今天能有工作做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.15,0:22:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,855)}是啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,==========Preview==========
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.20,0:23:58.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 快来救救咱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.87,0:24:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈 你变成蓬蓬头了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.66,0:24:04.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,静电太厉害结果就变成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.33,0:24:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还挺适合你的 就这样不也挺好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.54,0:24:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说傻话了 夏也来帮帮忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.26,0:24:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.34,0:24:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 电到了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.55,0:24:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.93,0:24:14.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 拜这个所赐我想到了个好点子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.01,0:24:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是电所以脑袋里的灯泡亮了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.47,0:24:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.10,0:24:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷霆般的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.64,0:24:20.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是蓬蓬头的哈比
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.98,0:24:22.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那干脆就叫蓬蓬比怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.48,0:24:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 名字什么的怎么样都无所谓啦
